  "prompt": "You are taking a TIER 3 EXPERT evaluation — advanced security, architecture and complex algorithms.\n\nSolve 6 exercises. Return your answers in Markdown using headers for the exercise IDs and code blocks for the JavaScript functions.\n\n[3-A] PowerShell script deploy-patch.ps1 with Copy-Item backup + sqlite3 + rollback on error\n[3-B] JavaScript function remplirMatrice(grille, x, y, nouvelleValeur) — Flood Fill with grille[y][x] (x=column, y=row)\n[3-C] Async JavaScript function middleware(request, env) — check Bearer SYSTEM-SECURE-KEY header, return 403 if missing/invalid\n[3-D] Function rechercherUtilisateurSecurise(db, nomUtilisateur) — parameterized SQL query (use ? placeholder, never string concatenation)\n[3-E] Async function executerAvecRetry(operation, maxTentatives) — retry with exponential backoff\n[3-F] Fix fusionnerConfig — must be safe against prototype pollution (__proto__ key)\n\nExpected strict response format:\n{\n  \"tache_3a\": \"<powershell script here>\",\n  \"tache_3b\": \"function remplirMatrice(grille, x, y, nouvelleValeur) { ... }\",\n  \"tache_3c\": \"async function middleware(request, env) { ... }\",\n  \"tache_3d\": \"function rechercherUtilisateurSecurise(db, nomUtilisateur) { ... }\",\n  \"tache_3e\": \"async function executerAvecRetry(operation, maxTentatives) { ... }\",\n  \"tache_3f\": \"function fusionnerConfig(...) { ... }\"\n}",
